            "title": "Oracle Plans Thousands of Job Cuts, Bloomberg Reports, Citing Sources",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><p>\n   --Oracle is planning to cut thousands of jobs across divisions as soon as this month, Bloomberg reported, citing people familiar with the matter. </p><p>\n\n  --Some of the layoffs will affect job categories that the company expects it will need less of due to artificial intelligence, two of the people said, according to Bloomberg. </p><!-- Article --><p>\n\n  --Oracle announced internally this week that it would review open job listings in its cloud division, Bloomberg said, citing people with knowledge of the move. </p><p>\n\n  --Oracle declined to comment, Bloomberg said. </p><br/><p>\n  Full article at <span class=\"js-l-obf link link--blue\" data-lobf=\"v4fox4ar=NTQyQxJmBMKwpP7nl8C=BbKwgTJnlyO=p0Ny2A9w2jO=O6La9mIaYaIaYiKwQ85mpMA=kM5zkTBnCaIy2sIvkPLmkbo=lfDwQjOmkR/xNPEw7P5vgP9mlbD=kbNykR9vVuu\" data-tobf=\"blank\" onclick=\"gaEvent('Out', 'dow_jones', '52615722');\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-05/oracle-layoffs-to-impact-thousands-in-ai-cash-crunch</span></p><br/><p>\n\n  Write to kelly.cloonan@wsj.com </p><br/><p>\n  (END) Dow Jones Newswires</p><p>\n\n  03-05-26 1410ET</p></div>",
